## 2009: Compass + **Sass**
Turing-complete CSS!

<!-- slide -->

```scss
.grid-span {
  width: percentage(((3*4em) + (2*1em)) / ((12*4em) + (11*1em))); // 23.7288136%
  margin-right: percentage(1em / ((12*4em) + (11*1em))); // 01.6949153%
  padding-left: percentage(((1*4em) + (1*1em)) / ((12*4em) + (11*1em))); // 08.4745763%
}
```

